{
  "texts": [
    "B. EffectivenessHere we evaluate the effectiveness of DeGPT from multiple aspects.",
    "We first test DeGPT focusing on four metrics including MVR, ER, CR, and NR.",
    "They can reflect the efficacy of DeGPT from both the structure and semantic information aspects.",
    "Further, we analyze the different optimization types involved and the reasons for the failure of some cases.Overall Effectiveness.",
    "We evaluate the performance of DeGPT on our dataset containing decompiler output of nonstripped and stripped binaries from LeetCode, Mirai, Coreutils, and AudioFlux."
  ]
}